column1: # Name: Share of labour force with tertiary education, Female

# Definition: Share of females in the labour force age 15+ in tertiary education that either leads to a first university degree or an equivalent award and programmes leading to an advanced research qualification.
# Source: International Labour Organization (ILO) Key Indicators of the Labour Market (KILM)
# Data from the No Ceilings project: http://noceilings.org
# For more about the data, please visit http://noceilings.org/data
